'''Phonane Mimesis Studios''' was a corporation that manufactured animatronic puppets and other movable models. Their puppets were very lifelike in appearance. Because of this skill in design, the [[Khoss]] of [[Knylenn]] commissioned the company to create an intricate life-support system for the long dead Knylenn elder.

